metadata.name: Fetish Angel
metadata.description:
The important thing is...
...is how he stages the women.
Props are used in his countless portraits.
Theatrical elements.
Toys.
Mouths and hands.
Poses.

Roman's pictures are different. 
He loves to show emotions, desires, fetishes and secrets. 
No sterile clean graphics, no models with perfect bodies and flawless skin. 
That is too boring for him. 
Instead, he packs fantasies and stories into his pictures, which are sometimes allowed to be dark.
